# manim-server

Minimal FastAPI service for rendering Manim scenes and returning an MP4 in a single request.

## Setup

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install -e .
```

## Run

Because the main file is named `manim-test.py`, run it with an import-by-path launcher:

```bash
python -c "import importlib.util; import uvicorn; spec = importlib.util.spec_from_file_location('manim_test_app', 'manim-test.py'); module = importlib.util.module_from_spec(spec); spec.loader.exec_module(module); uvicorn.run(module.app, host='127.0.0.1', port=8000)"
```

## Endpoint

`POST /render`

Request body:

```json
{
  "code": "from manim import *\n\nclass MainScene(Scene):\n    def construct(self):\n        self.play(Write(Text('Hello')))\n",
  "scene_name": "MainScene",
  "quality": "m"
}
```
